Physical interfaces:-
-------------------------

| Device     | Interface              | Zone / Role | IP Address     | Purpose                          |
|------------|------------------------|-------------|----------------|----------------------------------|
| ASA        | GigabitEthernet0/0     | Outside     | 159.66.72.50   | Internet / WAN (IPsec underlay)  |
| Palo Alto  | ethernet1/1            | Untrust     | 10.2.1.4       | Internet-facing interface        |
